Defines settings for settings for Google Earth Engine download

Source: R/ingest_gee_bysite.R
ingest_gee_bysite.Rd

Returns a list of two data frames, one with data at original modis dates (df), and one interpolated to all days (ddf).

  df_siteinfo,
  start_date,
  end_date,

  varnam,
  productnam,

  period,
  python_path,
  gee_path,
  data_path,
